neural_nets:
NatureCNN(
  (cnn): Sequential(
    (0): Conv2d(3, 32, kernel_size=(6, 6), stride=(3, 3))
    (1): DropBlock2d(p=0.0, block_size=3, inplace=False)
    (2): BatchNorm2d(32, eps=1e-05, momentum=0.1, affine=True, track_running_stats=True)
    (3): ReLU()
    (4): Conv2d(32, 64, kernel_size=(3, 3), stride=(2, 2))
    (5): DropBlock2d(p=0.0, block_size=3, inplace=False)
    (6): BatchNorm2d(64, eps=1e-05, momentum=0.1, affine=True, track_running_stats=True)
    (7): ReLU()
    (8): Conv2d(64, 64, kernel_size=(3, 3), stride=(1, 1))
    (9): DropBlock2d(p=0.0, block_size=3, inplace=False)
    (10): BatchNorm2d(64, eps=1e-05, momentum=0.1, affine=True, track_running_stats=True)
    (11): ReLU()
    (12): Flatten(start_dim=1, end_dim=-1)
  )
  (linear): Sequential(
    (0): Linear(in_features=3136, out_features=512, bias=True)
    (1): ReLU()
  )
)
